tomllib.md
     1→# `tomllib` – Tomli in the standard library
     2→
     3→Tomli was added to the Python standard library in Python 3.11.
     4→
     5→Relevant links:
     6→
     7→- Python Issue Tracker: https://bugs.python.org/issue40059
     8→- Tomli issue tracker: https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/issues/141
     9→- Discussion on PyPA "blessing" a TOML parser and/or including one in the standard library: https://discuss.python.org/t/adopting-recommending-a-toml-parser/4068
    10→- Python Enhancement Proposal: https://peps.python.org/pep-0680
    11→- CPython pull request: https://github.com/python/cpython/pull/31498
    12→
    13→## Converting Tomli to tomllib
    14→
    15→### Sync status
    16→
    17→`tomllib` in CPython commit https://github.com/python/cpython/commit/deaf509e8fc6e0363bd6f26d52ad42f976ec42f2
    18→matches Tomli commit https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/commit/7e563eed5286b5d46b8290a9f56a86d955b23a9a
    19→
    20→### Steps to convert
    21→
    22→- Move everything in `tomli:src/tomli` to `cpython:Lib/tomllib`. Exclude `py.typed`.
    23→
    24→- Remove `__version__ = ...` line from `cpython:Lib/tomllib/__init__.py`
    25→
    26→- Move everything in `tomli:tests` to `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib`. Exclude the following test data dirs recursively:
    27→
    28→  - `tomli:tests/data/invalid/_external/`
    29→  - `tomli:tests/data/valid/_external/`
    30→
    31→- Create `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib/__main__.py`:
    32→
    33→  ```python
    34→  import unittest
    35→
    36→  from . import load_tests
    37→
    38→
    39→  unittest.main()
    40→  ```
    41→
    42→- Add the following to `cpython:Lib/test/test_tomllib/__init__.py`:
    43→
    44→  ```python
    45→  import os
    46→  from test.support import load_package_tests
    47→
    48→
    49→  def load_tests(*args):
    50→      return load_package_tests(os.path.dirname(__file__), *args)
    51→  ```
    52→
    53→  Also change `import tomli as tomllib` to `import tomllib`.
    54→
    55→- In `cpython:Lib/tomllib/_parser.py` replace `__fp` with `fp` and `__s` with `s`. Add the `/` to `load` and `loads` function signatures.
